# Skill: PR Topic Finder — Repository Digest

This skill scans the entire Zamesin-Academy-Team repository and produces a structured digest of Ivan's best material. The PR manager loads this digest into Claude.ai to brainstorm article topics and theses for specific media outlets.

Runs fresh every time — no caching, no stale data.

## Input

Optional: outlet name and/or URL.
If provided — the digest will flag which materials are most relevant for that outlet's audience.
If not provided — produces a general digest of the strongest current material.

